{# v2 attribute_table: input is a list of attribute objects with `key`, `brief`,
   `requirement_level`, `provenance`, etc. directly inlined. Provenance is null
   for imported attributes; name_with_link reads it to pick the right link. #}
{% macro generate(attributes) -%}
{%- if attributes | length > 0 -%}
**Attributes:**

| Key | Stability | [Requirement Level]({{ links.requirement_level_url() }}) | Value Type | Description | Example Values |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
